{
  "stem": "12051.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, that was absolutely unbelievable, how he tortured people, how he destroyed human lives, how used the women for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] exploring things to do.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just can't even think of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That gives me a great satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm only sorry my father didn't live to see it, because he was a big Zionist.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the beginning, when they had the debates about-- in the Security Council, at that time, at Lake Success, because the UN didn't exist yet-- we were there at every meeting, David and I.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were there when the United States recognized the state of Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a jubilant moment in my life, and at the same time, great despair that my family didn't live to see that-- that we finally, whether it's the blood of the 6 million that created it, whether it's the conscience of the world that created the state of Israel, it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm upset what's going on now, but show me one country in the world that is winning a war that you didn't start and is giving back territories.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There is no such as.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Russia didn't give back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Germany didn't give back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is no country in the world that just is told by others, give back so you will have peace.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What kind of a peace is that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're negotiating with whom?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With a criminal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are coming to square one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We're starting all over again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "How about your children?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How do they how do they reconcile things with-- how do they live with the memories that you have, actually?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See what it is-- they can't have the same memories, because they didn't know the people, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't have the same link with the past as I have.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
